{"tid":2042932,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"實用工程admin提出以十萬元保釋 遭蘇文隆拒絕","createTime":"2020-05-30T05:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T11:10:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d8fb22780d37c026a0b419a4ff26ba5ac35a7fc4","tid":2042932,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"警方發現有人透過通訊軟件Telegram群組，發放武器的製作教學，事後拘捕群組其中1名管理員，指他涉發訊息教導他人「對付」水炮車和損毀交通燈，控告他煽惑他人有意圖傷人和煽惑他人刑事損壞兩罪，案件今早(30日)在粉嶺法院提訊，被告毋須答辯。裁判官蘇文隆將案押後至8月3日再訊，以待警方繼續調查，期間被告還押。<br />\n<br />\n28歲被告報稱工程師，控罪指他於去年11月17日和21日，煽惑Telegram使用者有意圖而傷害他人，以及破壞財產。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被告涉在Telegram發文，教導他人用泥封住水炮車的「柏葉」，藉此焗死裏面的警察，以及圖文並茂教人如何打爛交通燈。警方調查後拘捕被告，發現他兩部手機和桌上電腦均可在Telegram發文。辯方提出以現金10萬港元保釋，最終被駁回。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 東網"},{"pid":"5a5fffa520a06585698efee0a43d48edd2476d2e","tid":2042932,"uid":328890,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:40:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cd8f180d94a0a880a778d4a6165ffa523f5ea3d","tid":2042932,"uid":328890,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7fcf062eaaa3affa367002ba425ae6443b9ce83","tid":2042932,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cd8f180d94a0a880a778d4a6165ffa523f5ea3d","tid":2042932,"uid":328890,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb17e652708d367985b1bfba1072c72df139a54f","tid":2042932,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5fffa520a06585698efee